    \n                \n                \n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </li>   \n        <li class=\"title\">\n\n            <a class=\"a\" href=\"../../tzgg.htm\" title=\"通知公告\"><h3>通知公告</h3></a><i></i>\n        </li>   \n    </ul>\n</nav>\n<section class=\"nav_mask\"></section>\n\n<!--============================头部 结束=============================-->\n\n\n<!--============================主体 开始=============================-->\n\n<section id=\"banner\" class=\"banner\">\n     <ul class=\"slow_miso miso-initialized miso-slider\">\n        <div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"miso-list draggable\"><div class=\"miso-track\" role=\"listbox\" style=\"opacity: 1; width: 1280px; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);\"><li class=\"miso-slide miso-current miso-active\" data-miso-index=\"0\" aria-hidden=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"option\" aria-describedby=\"miso-slide00\" style=\"width: 1280px;\">\n <a tabindex=\"0\">\n            <img src=\"../../images/banner/ban7ner.jpg\" alt=\"\"> </a>\n        </li></div></div>\n    </ul> \n\n</section>\n<script>\n$(\".banner ul\").miso({\n    dots:true\n});\n</script>\n\n<section class=\"miso_content\">\n\n<section class=\"n_container n_lvli_detail\">\n    <div class=\"w1200\">\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"bg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"content_li\">\n                <div class=\"title001\">\n                    <h3>\n\n\n\n研究系列</h3>\n                </div>\n \n             \n                <div class=\"fl00 fl01 clearfix\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format4.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"left fl\">\n                        <div class=\"img slow fl\">\n                                                    <img src=\"/__local/9/DA/7A/537C7635C76B1BBC0C1784EF1AC_542939F0_ADC7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: #39b54a 3px solid;\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"con fr\">\n                            <h3>刘玲瑜</h3>\n                            <dl><dd>清华大学基础医学院，助理研究员</dd>\n                            \n                            </dl>                            \n                            <p>\n                                <b>Contact Us：</b><br>\n                              \n                                E-mail:  liulingyu@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn<br>\n                                Address：中国北京市海淀区清华大学郑裕彤楼D206\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"right fr\">\n \n       \n\n       \n\n\n\n\n<div id=\"vsb_content_4\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<div>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">教育背景</h4>\n <p>2007-2012中南大学湘雅医学院临床医学 学士</p>\n <p>2012-2019北京大学医学部神经生物学系神经生物学 医学博士</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">工作经历</h4>\n <p>2019-2022 清华大学生命科学学院 博士后</p>\n <p>2022-2024 清华大学医学院 助理研究员</p>\n <p>2024-至今 清华大学基础医学院 助理研究员</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">研究领域</h4>\n <p>我们围绕人体及模式生物的生理和病理学机制，就电磁辐射对生物体及生物结构的影响及其相互作用的课题方向，开展了电磁波对小鼠睡眠影响机制的课题探索。运用神经科学研究必须的生化技术（WB和组化等）、电生理技术（脑片膜片钳、在体单通道电生理、在体多通道技术、化学遗传学和光遗传学技术）和行为学检测（动物疼痛和抑郁样行为等）等。</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">科学贡献</h4>\n <p>本课题组发现长时间暴露于由100-Hz方波脉冲调制的2.4-GHz电磁辐射(EMR)在非热输出水平会导致小鼠清醒时间显著增加，且EMR对睡眠行为的改变不仅取决于载波频率，还取决于调制的频率和模式。这些结果暗示了EMR可能通过特定的生物感应机制引起一系列的生物学效应，引起了业内的广泛关注和认可。</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">荣誉奖励</h4>\n <p>2007-2008 国家奖学金、中南大学优秀学生干部；</p>\n <p>2008-2009 国家励志奖学金、中南大学优秀学生；</p>\n <p>2009-2010 中南大学优秀学生干部；</p>\n <p>2010-2011 中南大学优秀共产党员；</p>\n <p>2013-2014 北京大学基础医学院一等奖学金；</p>\n <p>2015-2016 北京大学三好学生。</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">代表性论文</h4>\n <p>1.Hu Deng<sup>1</sup>, Lingyu Liu<sup>1</sup>, Xiaping Tang, Yingxian Lu, Xiaofei Wang, Yanyu Zhao, Yigong Shi. Impact of specific electromagnetic radiation on wakefulness in mice. PNAS. 2024.121(15):e2313903121.</p>\n <p>2.Lingyu Liu<sup>1</sup>, Hu Deng<sup>1</sup>, Xiaping Tang<sup>1</sup>, Yingxian Lu, Jiayao Zhou, Xiaofei Wang, Yanyu Zhao, Bing Huang, Yigong Shi, Specific electromagnetic radiation in the wireless signal range increases wakefulness in mice, PNAS, 2021.118(31):e2105838118.</p>\n <p>3.Lingyu Liu, Ruiling Zhang, Lin Chen, Hongyan Zhao, Jiakang Wang, Daqing Guo, Jie Cai, Yanjun Cui, Guogang Xing, Chronic stress exacerbates neuropathic pain via the ACC-BLA pathway activation, Experimental neurology, 2019.313: p.109–123.</p>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">4.Mingjia Li<sup>1</sup>, Lingyu Liu<sup>1</sup>, Lin Chen<sup>1</sup>, Jie Cai, You Wan and Guogang Xing. Chronic stress exacerbates neuropathic pain via the integration of stress-affect-related information with nociceptive information in the central nucleus of the amygdala, Pain, 2017.158(4): p.717-739.</p>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n      \n\n</form>\n\n                      \n                    </div>\n                                      \n                </div>\n          <section class=\"n_sanji\">\n<ul style=\"    height: 44px;\">\n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\" title=\"教职员工\">教职员工</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/jzjs.htm\" title=\"兼职教授\">兼职教授</a></li>\n</ul>\n                  \n                </section>\n\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"mianbao\">\n            <div>\n     您现在的位置： \n                        <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\">师资队伍</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\">基础医学院</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy/yjxl.htm\">研究系列</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                正文\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content_li1\"></div>\n        </div>\n    \n</section>\n<script>\n$('.miso_hd ul').miso({\n    autoplay:false,\n    slidesToShow: 3,\n    waitForAnimate: false,\n    asNavFor:$('.miso_bd')\n});\n$('.miso_bd').miso({\n    autoplay:false,\n    waitForAnimate: false,\n    adaptiveHeight:true,\n    asNavFor:$('.miso_hd ul')\n});\n</script>\n\n\n</section>\n\n<!--============================主体 结束=============================-->\n\n\n<!--============================底部 开始=============================-->\n\n\n<footer class=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"w1200 clearfix\">\n        <div class=\"center fl\">\n    <a><img src=\"../../images/logo1.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-height: 55px;\"></a>\n\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"right fr\">\n    <img src=\"../../style/0FE8A93F7C0CB67D3DB1C572B99_8836C5CA_2118.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"left fl\">\n            <div class=\"top\">\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/mp4video.js\"></script>\n<p> 清华大学内西北门往南100米医学科学楼 <br>邮编：100084<br>电话：010-62792995<br>邮箱：bmsyb@tsinghua.edu.cn </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"bottom\">\n<!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<p>Copyright © 2024 清华大学基础医学院</p>\n\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</footer>\n\n<div class=\"dt-arrow\" id=\"gotop\"><svg t=\"1621638623727\" class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 1024 1024\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" p-id=\"44856\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\"><path d=\"M943 16H81a65 65 0 0 0-65 65v862a65 65 0 0 0 65 65h862a65 65 0 0 0 65-65V81a65 65 0 0 0-65-65zM755.59 576.36a21 21 0 0 1-29.67 1.29L533 400.79v389.75a21 21 0 0 1-42 0V400.68l-192.92 177a21 21 0 0 1-28.39-31l242.23-222.2L754.3 546.69a21 21 0 0 1 1.29 29.67zM752 254.46H272a21 21 0 0 1 0-42h480a21 21 0 0 1 0 42z\" p-id=\